{"tid":2338659,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"遭左報發功誣陷任人唯親 司法機構發稿反駁任命程序符合《基本法》","createTime":"2020-12-24T07:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T07:22:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f09d82bdd0f3c919bb6a5b0132aa61f84addbbd5","tid":2338659,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uqOkX-JAyORWCdN_vW5cFRQ_nF4=/802x1334/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2JA4NQMSVNHQ3PFNZAQOFGCHRE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuqOkX-JAyORWCdN_vW5cFRQ_nF4%3D%2F802x1334%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2JA4NQMSVNHQ3PFNZAQOFGCHRE.png&h=bc10b877&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《大公報》上月初引述2014年時任《南華早報》記者Howard Winn一篇裁判官指控任命體制的報道，以「有法不依曾引發多名裁判官辭職抗議」、「升遷任人唯親司法步向『獨大』」為題，撰寫報道批評司法機構，稱「黃絲法官被公眾投訴仍獲升級加薪」，令公眾質疑任命標準。報道又引述退休裁判官、現為大律師的黃汝榮批評，當年升職面試時只有5名「推薦委員會委員」列席，與條例列明委員會決議至少有7名委員不符。<br />\n<br />\n反送中運動後警方及律政司大肆檢控參與的示威者，令法庭判決成為輿論焦點。左報上月發功炮轟司法機構「有法不依」、「任人唯親」，司法機構今日表示就傳媒關注法官及司法人員的招聘程序，說明任命的既定程序，強調所有任命及專業資格均符合《基本法》及相關規定，並由特首據司法人員推薦委員會的推薦作出，「這是個行之有效及嚴格依法處理的機制。」<br />\n<br />\n司法機構表示，會定期公開招聘填補高等法院原訟法庭法官、區域法院法官和常任裁判官的空缺，每次均在網頁及報章登廣告。所有申請提交遴選委員會考慮，該會由終審法院首席法官委任、法官及司法人員組成，按法例詳細審視每名應徵者的履歷。遴選面試和會議有推薦委員會成員以觀察員身分列席，所有任命評估都會呈交推薦委員會考慮。上訴法院法官、各法院領導及其他行政管理工作的司法職位，則只考慮由具司法經驗的現職人員出任，終院首席法官經諮詢後會內部建議人選，獲提名人選亦會呈交推薦委員會考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201224/QIOHN2LPIZGJZF6I7P2H4I6T7A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201224%2FQIOHN2LPIZGJZF6I7P2H4I6T7A%2F&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MTmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=46fd0846\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201224%2FQIOHN2LPIZGJZF6I7P2H4I6T7A%2F&h=f19a9c5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201224/QIOHN2LPIZGJZF6I7P2H4I6T7A/</a>"},{"pid":"27eae21c63eac553e99c8a2e62d6ea867ac88ee6","tid":2338659,"uid":25797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:04:14.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦 兩公婆床頭打交床尾和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb288b55aa66762912996e8258f254b49700ac67","tid":2338659,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63c9093334a1d907c5ad6d3fc55421157bfea9bf","tid":2338659,"uid":374427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T07:22:00.000Z","msg":"一陣活動要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[重post] 平安夜活動要人!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2337539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2337539</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}